response.original_title: AIX Records Blu-Ray HD-Audio Video Sampler IV
response.overview: The technology of recording in real surround HD-Audio coupled with the capability of the blu-ray format to deliver HD-Video brings the intimacy of the performance into your own personal listening space. Watch it with the video or simply sit back and revel in the music as it is passed between members of the group.
